{"tid":2318341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"你的堅持 我畢生受用","createTime":"2020-12-09T09:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T09:23:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c13dfee1de939c2ba1c0a35b333423db5c3e9059","tid":2318341,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=c3cec9af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&h=fa7b1bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n你的堅持 我畢生受用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY=/1772x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY%3D%2F1772x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg&h=14a205de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有《蘋果日報》員工依創刊電視廣告繪圖，盼黎智英仍像25年前般，&ldquo;No fear we have to fight on.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n黎智英昨天在收押所度過73歲生日，也是他被關押的第六天。連日來香港人送上的祝福從無間斷，有掛念他的手足、有嚮往公平公義的年輕人，也有同業的共勉。有讀者更打趣叫「肥佬黎」在收押所化身「記者」發掘「猛料」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「佢唔諗自己，只睇點樣幫大家」<br />\n<br />\n祝福以外，更多人感謝黎智英以生命影響生命。有讀者從《蘋果日報》、《壹週刊》中學懂反思，分辨是非；有年輕人牢記黎智英說過不移民、不離開，也決心留在香港。有海外留學生從沒忘記黎智英在香港最艱難時刻的堅持，「對我來說是畢生受用」。<br />\n<br />\n每一封寄給黎智英的信，都在訴說一個故事。有大學生說，小時候父親每天都買《蘋果日報》，一買就多年，去年更與父親一起訂閱蘋果，「自由有價，自然新聞也應有價」。他說一直都希望為香港做些事，但在今日香港，會思考自己的付出是否值得，「在極度壓迫的環境下為求生存而放棄的是否值得」。<br />\n<br />\n當眼見很多同學朋友都移民外地，他卻記得黎智英在訪問中說過不移民、不離開，不久前他便決心留在香港，「黎先生，蘋果在香港人爭取民主、自由與真相的道路上從沒缺席。而你本人也對香港不離不棄。自然，當您身受牢獄之災時，港人也必定不會放棄您、放棄自己、放棄香港，如此黎先生也可放心。希望上主憐恤眾人，保守您和其他入獄手足的身體健康。願能早日相見」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw=/777x904/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw%3D%2F777x904%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif&h=36ccb19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一如既往 不會屈服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws=/606x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws%3D%2F606x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif&h=e197a0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nProud of you, as always<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0=/674x826/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0%3D%2F674x826%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif&h=ce3f7a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝安寧度過黑暗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE=/590x755/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE%3D%2F590x755%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif&h=0c152137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上帝與你同在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Te9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA=/706x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTe9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA%3D%2F706x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif&h=7a91269e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當權者良心泯滅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig=/701x478/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig%3D%2F701x478%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif&h=820f9249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人永遠在你身邊"}]}